high_descs: Turn around and walk to the black table.
Pick up the spoon that's behind the fork on the table.
Turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Put the spoon inside of the black bowl on the counter.
Pick up the black bowl from the counter.
Turn left and walk back to the black table.
Place the bowl on the table.
anns.task_desc: To put a spoon in a bowl and place it on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the oven, then turn left again and walk to the wall, turn left to face the round black table.
Pick up the spoon next to the egg on the round black table.
Walk over to the section of counter to the right of the oven.
Put the spoon in the bowl that is on the counter in front of you.
Pick up the bowl with the spoon in it off of the counter.
Turn left and walk back over to the round black table.
Put the bowl with the spoon in it on the table to the left of the closest large metal knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a spoon in it on a round black table.

high_descs: Go to the black table
Pick up the spoon
Go to the right of the stove
Put the spoon in the bowl
Pick up the bowl
Go to the black table
Place the bowl down
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon in a bowl and place on the table
